{"tid":430961,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【慎入】人妻食精液奶昔 割屄唇當頸鍊戴","createTime":"2017-10-10T09:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T11:37:05.000Z","uid":144430,"like":11,"dislike":113,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"c2992cf73c4800bdaa55169a7e7c0fcb5c3b7a3f","tid":430961,"uid":144430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"網紅Tracy Kiss育有兩個細路<br />\n佢嘅出位行為令佢備受關注<br />\n<br />\n而繼食精液奶昔後<br />\n哩位人妻於上年12月嘅時候曾做過陰唇手術<br />\n將過多嘅陰唇割除<br />\n術後更將陰唇放入防腐液中保存留念<br />\n<br />\n先打格<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/55/80/qaCRpJ_cl5_YqKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F55%2F80%2FqaCRpJ_cl5_YqKQ.jpg&h=ca01815e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n【警告:以下内容可能導致部份人不安,請慎入】<br />\n&gt;&gt;原圖連結:<a href=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/55/80/qaCRpJ_cl5_YqKSX.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F55%2F80%2FqaCRpJ_cl5_YqKSX.jpg&d=exzgDcy%2FDcOGJU%2F3kcsv9L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=effb0758\" target=\"_blank\">https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/55/80/qaCRpJ_cl5_YqKSX.jpg</a>&lt;&lt;<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n但所謂不孝有三,無圖為大<br />\n不如一齊睇佢嘅頸鍊嘅製作過程吧<br />\n<br />\n<strong>首先</strong>將陰唇自然陰乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.stayathomemum.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/vag2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stayathomemum.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fvag2a.png&h=32ecaea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>然後</strong>喺陰唇上上色<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.stayathomemum.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/vag2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stayathomemum.com.au%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fvag2b.png&h=bc63a942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s.newsweek.com/sites/www.newsweek.com/files/styles/embed-lg/public/2017/10/02/1002labia010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.newsweek.com%2Fsites%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fembed-lg%2Fpublic%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F1002labia010.jpg&h=4dbabf79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>最後</strong>用吹風機吹乾後再倒入樹脂後就可以定型<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2017/55/80/qaCRpJ_cl5_YqKs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2017%2F55%2F80%2FqaCRpJ_cl5_YqKs.jpg&h=7152e475&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>完成</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s.newsweek.com/sites/www.newsweek.com/files/styles/embed-lg/public/2017/10/02/10-02labia-necklace-tracy01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.newsweek.com%2Fsites%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fembed-lg%2Fpublic%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F10-02labia-necklace-tracy01.jpg&h=7ded3d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2017/09/29/15/44BD6B3400000578-4921956-image-a-12_1506693616797.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2017%2F09%2F29%2F15%2F44BD6B3400000578-4921956-image-a-12_1506693616797.jpg&h=bb4ddd46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n片源:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IVDmavpzZ3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIVDmavpzZ3A&d=exzgDcy%2FDcOGJU%2F3kcsv9L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=ad5467ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IVDmavpzZ3A</a><br />\n事主YouTube channel:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGqWP3kL24hgHuQ5v28azEQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCGqWP3kL24hgHuQ5v28azEQ&d=exzgDcy%2FDcOGJU%2F3kcsv9L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=b5c0dacd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGqWP3kL24hgHuQ5v28azEQ</a><br />\n原文:<a href=\"https://news.gamme.com.tw/1525580\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gamme.com.tw%2F1525580&d=exzgDcy%2FDcOGJU%2F3kcsv9L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=bd01a852\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.gamme.com.tw/1525580</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.stayathomemum.com.au/news-of-the-day/mum-turns-her-labia-into-a-piece-of-jewellery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stayathomemum.com.au%2Fnews-of-the-day%2Fmum-turns-her-labia-into-a-piece-of-jewellery%2F&d=exzgDcy%2FDcOGJU%2F3kcsv9L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=4a8391c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.stayathomemum.com.au/news-of-the-day/mum-turns-her-labia-into-a-piece-of-jewellery/</a>"},{"pid":"e09fb83961c8cc4b36a1f9d3a2dd9ad32cf23c13","tid":430961,"uid":144430,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:24:52.000Z","msg":"事主IG:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tracykissdotcom/?hl=zh-tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftracykissdotcom%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-tw&d=exzgDcy%2FDcOGJU%2F3kcsv9L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=73399aa4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tracykissdotcom/?hl=zh-tw</a>"},{"pid":"5f62d55bd22e56b0a254738249d76b00f6c4dddf","tid":430961,"uid":85819,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:26:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dd85ee070e394ab33cf79e5ad23b78ad8e8477b","tid":430961,"uid":20658,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:29:05.000Z","msg":"陰唇保平安，好過你帶佛牌"},{"pid":"a01a7b3c2e711a911f62059732b70c7ef8b8e496","tid":430961,"uid":144430,"like":14,"dislike":9,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T09:30:34.000Z","msg":"【再續】精液奶昔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://amebobook.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/tmp_8447-ad_22597532911536120980.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Famebobook.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2Ftmp_8447-ad_22597532911536120980.jpg&h=a008ae13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://amebobook.com/wp-content/uploa